Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三重加速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四重加速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是東之神速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她正是我們East•Genetics的三年級的學年第一
